        "TileImage": "$($repository 729aa28f-5856-449a-9e41-3e4fedc5c38f).Image",
        "Description": "Good afternoon, 47.\r\rAnother Friday, another five individuals who have found themselves on the wrong side of our clients.\r\rThe terms remain unchanged. You are to eliminate the targets while remaining in your suit. No other special requirements, no preferred methods of execution.\r\rConsider this a routine conclusion to the week, I know it has been rough with those monday pirates. \r\rEnjoy the freedom.\r\rGood luck.",
